cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.DB, cs.SE 

The paper discusses the challenges of conditioning in data fusion systems in big-data environments, which involves both soft and hard sources. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including artificial intelligence (cs.AI) for probabilistic inferencing, machine learning (cs.LG) for evidence updating, data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) for stream processing, databases (cs.DB) for data fusion, and software engineering (cs.SE) for parameter selection.
